5475","card_id":"Q_9168211532","target":{"id":9168211532,"title":"大学生该不该超前消费?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/9168211532","type":"question","created":1736422981,"answer_count":56,"follower_count":60,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1746],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"“大学生应该超前消费” 我觉得啊，在如今的社会环境下，大学生适度超前消费没什么问题。 你想啊，大学生有时会碰到一些突发状况或者紧急需求。比如说突然生病得去看病，或者电脑坏了影响学习和完成作业，这时候适度超前消费就能马上解决难题。 还有呢，大学生正处在成长和发展的关键阶段。超前消费能让他们有机会获得一些对自己很重要的资源。就像参加那种行业里最新的学术研讨会，或者买专业相关的优质网课，如果因为当时钱不够就不去做，说不定就错过了特别好的发展机会。 另外，超前消费能帮助大学生培养信用意识和理财能力。只要他们合理规划，按时还钱，就能更明白信用有多重要，也能学会怎么管理自己的钱，这对他们以后进入社会可有帮助啦。"},"attached_info":"CkAIpMP9pp38yc8cEAMaCTExMjgxMDE3NiDF7P67BjAAODxAB3IKOTE2ODIxMTUzMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"63 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1736540470.516131","card_id":"Q_5288207233","target":{"id":5288207233,"title":"游戏音乐有多重要？为什么一款游戏通关后，音乐往往能成为玩家记忆中最深刻的部分？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/5288207233","type":"question","created":1732693895,"answer_count":19,"follower_count":37,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3781351],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIpMP9pp38yc8cEAMaCTExMjAzNDExMCCHn5u6BjAAOCVACHIKNTI4ODIwNzIzM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"9_1736540470.516341","card_id":"Q_9211151442","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":9211151